	NIMS - Home






















The  Exer-Rest® technology is based upon a patented process called Whole Body  Periodic Acceleration (WBPA). NIMS has extensive research demonstrating the  benefits of using the Exer-Rest® as an aid to:

Temporarily increase local circulation
Provide temporary relief of minor aches and pains
Support local muscle relaxation
Reduce morning stiffness



Exer-Rest®  is marketed under the classification regulation Title 21 of the Code of Federal  Regulations (CFR) 890.5975 of the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act.
